fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0f01ca57e61bcba7c1a620c7a333ed37241cbe","tid":396230,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家啲人為左個萬幾蚊搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係做奴隸</blockquote><br />\n如果搵少啲可以少啲勾心鬥角 我肯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知為乜，又冇so</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華人劣等基因造成<br />\n啲撚樣玩走左人老世會加你人工咩唔通<br />\n收萬幾蚊做完野咪hea咯<br />\n所以多華人既公司永遠都係垃圾"},{"pid":"6429e00ac83c6d981eaaeb3bea385b60e7e17f4e","tid":396230,"uid":15814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家啲人為左個萬幾蚊搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係做奴隸</blockquote><br />\n如果搵少啲可以少啲勾心鬥角 我肯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知為乜，又冇so</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華人劣等基因造成<br />\n啲撚樣玩走左人老世會加你人工咩唔通<br />\n收萬幾蚊做完野咪hea咯<br />\n所以多華人既公司永遠都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n咪係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你講中晒我想講既point<br />\n細個都係一齊抄功課hea 9老師架嘛<br />\n點解大個左就唔可以咁?一樣齊心少少搞掂晒啲野仲快啦唉"},{"pid":"6f256e2ed200b262330bab4f0306a95ed87ab98b","tid":396230,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c481c6920a97c3458cc9d560b884e3540a84fc","tid":396230,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6138dbef85127700f18ee9236fe7dee094c7593e","tid":396230,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:57:57.000Z","msg":"長期冇表情,真係好笑先笑"},{"pid":"25761959f2a33e88face29ed49af747c4e5307b4","tid":396230,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:00:42.000Z","