緊宜家呢份pt已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前有份cafe pt同班同事熟真係互發脾氣大家都唔介意 講晒粗口互屌都咁fd 宜家呢份乜都硬食 對同事啲語氣又唔敢太串 就算憎一個人都要笑笑口同佢扮fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人生真係險惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd422e5f4ca70c59de459c2aaa8da9575297e16","tid":396230,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>返工一向唔點笑<br />\n理撚理班人</blockquote><br />\n新人唔笑嘅話條路會好難行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔刷鞋都要學下附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得最多係「好」「ok」同「明白」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3db777b2e7882df094211972e6f9d95076e69ea","tid":396230,"uid":15814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}